  "description": "Is A Banking Product that enables the extension or renewal of a financial obligation or investment beyond its original maturity.\r\n\r\nA type of financial arrangement that allows the outstanding amount (such as a loan, deposit, or investment) to be carried forward into a new term under predefined conditions, including updated interest rates, duration, and repayment or settlement terms.\r\n\r\nComment:\r\nRollover Service contains the operational capabilities that allow a financial product (loan, term deposit, credit facility, etc.) to be renewed or extended at maturity.",
